d share it with another user inside owncloud's web interface.\r\n2. share this item with another user. \r\n3. rename the item\r\n4. login as the user you shared the item with\r\n\r\n## result ##\r\nthe user sees the item with its original name\r\n\r\n## expected outcome ##\r\nthe file name should update\r\n\r\n## affected versions ##\r\noc 5 stable up to 5.0.10 / oc 6 master. did not test oc 4.5 \r\n\r\nsince i am working my way into core development, i'd like to fix this bite size thing myself. i'd be grateful for any pointers how to approach this. i presume that a hook might be the best option?\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"mtgap","id":1097106,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/454a73ee5feeb428d0c163a48903332c?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f52d29a66f285a1d61125dd69ac0766b2.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"454a73ee5feeb428d0c163a48903332c","url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap","html_url":"https://github.com/mtgap","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false}}